			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Using sepiolite and quicklime as passivation agents, applying them to heavy metal contaminated soil to reduce the mobility of heavy metals in the soil and enhance the soil's adsorption capacity for heavy metals, thereby reducing the bioavailability of heavy metals in the soil.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">使用海泡石、生石灰作为钝化药剂，施加到重金属污染土壤中，降低土壤中重金属的流动性，并增强土壤对重金属的吸附能力，从而减少土壤中重金属的生物有效性。</common:generalComment>
